{"tid":894031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【商標權官司．短片】日媒暗訪國產「無印良品」：日本Muji在我們之後，是抄襲的","createTime":"2018-11-08T05:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T13:09:02.000Z","uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc8ebd18f977bab1a178d0e774d82cb5d635c9c","tid":894031,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181108/s00004/1541640242220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181108%2Fs00004%2F1541640242220&d=Ka4QYMh6GiHTsAA8ISVHEi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=00a62de1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181108%2Fs00004%2F1541640242220&h=dbe68017\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181108/s00004/1541640242220</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181108/s00004/69236de6d4dfbcb68ead934e411accd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181108%2Fs00004%2F69236de6d4dfbcb68ead934e411accd7.jpg&h=0cf1c07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1980年創立的日本生活用品店公司無印良品（Muji），早前於內地一場與國產「無印良品」的商標權官司中敗訴，部分商品未來或只能標示「Muji」，不能使用「無印良品」字眼，事件引起中日兩地社會爭議。日本傳媒ANN近日在一篇專題報道中，派記者前往國產「無印」暗中採訪，其間對方指「日本Muji在我們之後，是抄襲的」。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：國產「無印良品」告贏日本Muji 黨媒：本土無印良品店<br />\n<br />\n專題報道中，節目組將國產「無印」與日本「無印」兩者產品比對，發現無論衣服還是文具，其樣式設計風格都非常類似。他們又發現，國產「無印」產品質素十分參差，例如毛巾不但會脫毛，而且洗滌後會變色。另外，ANN記者上門暗中採訪國產「無印」位於北京公司的負責人，對方竟指「日本Muji在我們之後，是抄襲的」。<br />\n<br />\n這場「無印良品」商標權風波始於2000年，當時日本無印良品尚未進入內地，海南南華實業貿易公司則向商標局註冊「無印良品」文字商標，並在2004年轉讓給2000年成立的北京棉田紡織品。2011年，由北京棉田任股東的「北京無印」成立，並獲北京棉田授權在內地獨家使用有關商標。<br />\n<br />\n良品計劃2001年起向內地商標局提出異議但不果，2009年提起訴訟，同樣不成功。去年12月，北京棉田提出訴訟，法院裁定，日方在內地銷售的部分商品標識「錯誤使用」了北京「無印良品」商標，須向北京棉田支付約62萬元人民幣，並在門店發出侵權聲明，引起關注。良品計劃近日表示，將盡最大努力取回商標，又透露今年1月已提出上訴。"},{"pid":"e67bce0ba3eef3a522525ae1886e99875e00f55b","tid":894031,"uid":32077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbc4352908b6394f9c8d2546fe7bda691fb15c5","tid":894031,"uid":171832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"中國人又贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cce28aadaf514957673b4fae573be66aaa59128","tid":894031,"uid":35882,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7f7958bd5842fb41f286a3d55656eff1ad37ec","tid":894031,"uid":57065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係無良印品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415369e7fdf72ac194660845d79737b2d0e0cb6a","tid":894031,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"無印奶支 抵死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed384d928747ab23fed0c4a3e8165fc5cd831423","tid":894031,"uid":192189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"喬丹都嬴JORDAN啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240bded37bdf1015887bd52200e4016e160e6299","tid":894031,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"執哂所有大陸鋪頭，班大陸人自然會過日本買"},{"pid":"00f2d06bbfd51b4c6ad688df9abe2629444d4eb3","tid":894031,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"240bded37bdf1015887bd52200e4016e160e6299","tid":894031,"uid":28435,"like":